### Warenkorb-Zustand lesen (anfangs leer)
GET http://localhost:9000/v1/carts/123456789

### Artikel hinzufügen (empty -> active)
POST http://localhost:9000/v1/carts/123456788/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "p1",
  "name": "Scala Buch",
  "quantity": 1,
  "price": 39.9
}

### Weiteren Artikel hinzufügen
POST http://localhost:9000/v1/carts/123456789/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "p2",
  "name": "Kaffee",
  "quantity": 2,
  "price": 4.5
}

### Artikel entfernen
DELETE http://localhost:9000/v1/carts/123456789/items/p2

### Checkout (active -> checkedOut)
POST http://localhost:9000/v1/carts/123456789/checkout

### Nach Checkout: Hinzufügen wird ignoriert (bleibt checkedOut)
POST http://localhost:9000/v1/carts/123456789/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "p3",
  "name": "Tee",
  "quantity": 1,
  "price": 3.0
}
